<item>
            <title>[HADOOP-13700] Remove unthrown IOException from TrashPolicy#initialize and #getInstance signatures</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-13700</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;TrashPolicy is marked as public &amp;amp; evolving, but its public API, specifically TrashPolicy.getInstance() has been changed in an incompatible way. &lt;br/&gt;
1) The path parameter is removed in 3.0&lt;br/&gt;
2) A new IOException is thrown in 3.0&lt;/p&gt;</description>
